Used for deeper analysis.

Operator	Function
Invert	Reverse causal direction
Rescale	Change system resolution
Threshold	Detect phase change
Weave	Interlock multiple chains
Fuse	Hold apparent opposites
Relay	Multi-perspective reasoning
Canonize	Promote pattern to doctrine
Modulate	Adjust transformation intensity
Sample	Use representative slice
Name	Assign portable label
Permute	Reorder sequence
Substitute	Replace with equivalent part
Negate	Construct complement
Recursion	Apply transformation to itself


